,"value":253},"要把基础库依赖的 vxe-table 直接替换为 Element Plus 表格很不现实。在没做过表格调研的情况下就迁移基础组件是不可接受的，何况我们只想改个滚动条样式。",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":255,"children":256},{},[257],{"type":173,"value":258},"这是 ElTable 的示例。看着这漂亮的滚动条当时真是心痒痒呀！",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":260,"children":261},{},[262],{"type":167,"tag":214,"props":263,"children":266},{"alt":264,"src":265},"element-plus table","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20230218231215.png?w=60",[],{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":268,"children":269},{},[270,272,279],{"type":173,"value":271},"讲到 Element Plus，能不能用 ",{"type":167,"tag":181,"props":273,"children":276},{"href":274,"rel":275},"https://element-plus.gitee.io/zh-CN/component/scrollbar.html",[185],[277],{"type":173,"value":278},"ElScrollbar",{"type":173,"value":280}," 组件做点什么呢？",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":282,"children":283},{},[284],{"type":173,"value":285},"答案是否定的，因为 ElScrollbar 只能处理简单的滚动系统。",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":287,"children":288},{},[289],{"type":173,"value":290},"如图所示，假设 ElScrollbar 组件 S 本身高 400px，其直接子元素 Children 高 1000px。这个场景足够简单，所以能轻易获取 S 的滚动余量有 600px。",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":292,"children":293},{},[294],{"type":167,"tag":214,"props":295,"children":298},{"alt":296,"src":297},"Simple Scrollbar System","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20230219003509.png?w=50",[],{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":300,"children":301},{},[302],{"type":173,"value":303},"当组件有复杂的层级嵌套时，ElScrollbar 组件就不知道你要使用哪一个元素去计算滚动余量了。如图所示，在复杂情况下，ElScrollbar 的虚拟滚动条甚至会和原生滚动条出现冲突的情况。",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":305,"children":306},{},[307],{"type":167,"tag":214,"props":308,"children":311},{"alt":309,"src":310},"Complex Scrollbar System","https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20230219004750.png?w=50",[],{"type":167,"tag":168,"props":313,"children":315},{"id":314},"use-scrollbars-的诞生",[316],{"type":173,"value":317},"Use Scrollbars 的诞生",{"type":167,"tag":175,"props":319,"children":320},{},[321,323],{"type":173,"value":3